Lord, I pray that you would assure each one of us of your love and commitment to fulfill all that you've said to us.

455
00:33:31,380 --> 00:33:39,380
Lord, give us the faith to come to you with our struggles and the patience to wait.

456
00:33:39,380 --> 00:33:44,080
To see you bring about the good work you've promised in our lives.

457
00:33:44,080 --> 00:33:46,180
We pray this in Jesus name, amen.